data.description: LUXURY PRIVATE CUSTOM BUILT OASIS ON ALMOST A WHOLE ACRE IN THE CITY OF BONITA! THIS IS A 2,636 SQFT CUSTOM HOME, A DETACHED PERMITTED 336 SQFT STUDIO (ADU POTENITAL?) AND A 1350SQFT WAREHOUSE/SHOP ALL WITHIN YOUR OWN PRIVATE GATED ACCESS TO THIS GORGEOUS PROPERTY! THE MAIN HOME FEATURES A NEWLY REMODELED CHEF'S KITCHEN WITH A VIKING REFRIGERATOR, 6 BURNER STOVE, 2 OVENS (1 CONVECTION OVEN), WINE FRIDGE & MORE. THERE ARE 2 BEDROOMS AND AN OFFICE (OR OPTIONS 3RD BEDROOM) ON THE ENTRY LEVEL AND ANOTHER BEDROOM AND PRIMARY BEDROOM UPSTAIRS. THIS HOME IS PRIVACY AT ITS BEST! ADDITIONAL FEATURES INCLUDE FULLY PAID OFF SOLAR, DUAL AC UNITS (1 FOR EACH FLOOR OF LIVING SPACE), NO HOA, NO MELLO ROOS! AND YOU CAN ALSO TAKE ADVANTAGE OF THE ASSUMABLE LOAN AVAILABLE AT 2.375%.
